track_notes: Sommet de Nibles and Cloche de Barles... Starting from Le Forest... Nice trip...

This is a wonderfull place, for eyes and radio!
You must park on the small road (not so many room) near the Forest village where is a GSM pylone nearby. The track is easy (yellow paint; it could be some sheep and guard-dog. At the Col 1787m you must Climb some rocks to reach Sommet de Nibles (2 ways possible, easyer on the west-side); much more easy for the Cloche de Barles. The trig point is on the final crest, where you must behave for vertigo. Plenty room for antenna.

# 1/3 go to 364
# 2/3 go to 362
# 3/3 go back
